title: Funko Pop! Vinyl Daemon Targaryen - House of the Dragon NFT.
description: This Funko Pop! Vinyl figure is from the NFT Physical Pops 2023 series and features Daemon Targaryen from the popular fantasy television franchise House of the Dragon. It is an exclusive release by Funko, identified by MPN 77035 and UPC 0889698770354. The figure comes in box number 149 and belongs to the NFT Pop! Vinyl product line.
